# This is a placeholder for the FBX model file.
# The actual Battle Drone FBX model should be placed here.
# Since the uploaded FBX files cannot be read as text, this placeholder
# indicates where the model should be located in the file system.
# 
# The application will attempt to load the model from multiple possible paths:
# - /models/battle_drone.fbx
# - /attached_assets/uploads_files_3654680_Battle+Drone_1754177328485.fbx  
# - /attached_assets/uploads_files_3654680_Battle+Drone_1754177504862.fbx
#
# If the FBX model cannot be loaded, the application will automatically
# create a fallback procedural drone model for demonstration purposes.
